  "metaDescription": "A phased checklist for when an employee with access to trade secrets, key customers, or sensitive systems gives notice &mdash; covenant review, forensic imaging, access investigation, and relationship security.",
  "standfirst": "When someone with the keys gives notice &mdash; especially headed to a competitor, a customer, or their own new venture &mdash; the decisions that matter most get made in the first few days, often before anyone is thinking about litigation. The sequence below front-loads the steps that cannot be undone later.",
